Isn't that Xiaofang?

29
00:02:49,099 --> 00:02:49,819
It's Xiaofang

30
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:51,219
She looks great, sure

31
00:02:51,219 --> 00:02:51,819
but wearing so little

32
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:52,960
So gorgeous

33
