Sis, you're so cool!

36
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,639
Xiaofang

37
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:03,520
Xiaofang

38
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:05,319
You

39
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,219
You got your hair permed

40
00:03:07,479 --> 00:03:07,979
And what's

41
