95
00:04:44,439 --> 00:04:45,660
I'm here. I was just dodging my mom.

96
00:04:46,019 --> 00:04:47,060
Come on, hurry!

97
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:47,980
Come on, Sis.

98
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:48,879
Middle of the night,

99
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:50,180
