100
00:04:50,259 --> 00:04:50,720
Let me tell you,

101
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,019
I never knew till I got this perm.

102
00:04:52,220 --> 00:04:53,019
It's like wearing a fur coat

103
00:04:53,019 --> 00:04:53,959
