113
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:13,660
Fine.

114
00:05:14,779 --> 00:05:15,699
No need to owe me.

115
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,519
Skip the conditioner, just wash it.

116
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:21,019
You're really good with money, huh?

117
00:05:23,079 --> 00:05:23,860
Okay.

118
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:26,560
One lady guest, step outside please.

119
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:28,839
Why, you little...

120
00:05:28,839 --> 00:05:29,199
Let me tell you,

121
00:05:29,199 --> 00:05:30,199
