122
00:05:30,939 --> 00:05:32,759
Ripping off your own feels so good.

123
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,699
Keep it down.

124
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:40,680
Three.

125
00:05:41,220 --> 00:05:41,579
Two.

126
00:05:42,139 --> 00:05:42,519
One.

127
00:05:46,180 --> 00:05:46,579
Mom.

128
00:05:46,699 --> 00:05:47,439
Did you see that?

129
00:05:47,660 --> 00:05:48,560
