132
00:06:06,180 --> 00:06:06,680
Three.

133
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:07,639
Two.

134
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,459
One.

135
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:11,100
Three.

136
00:06:11,379 --> 00:06:11,800
