137
00:06:12,459 --> 00:06:12,819
Mom.

138
00:06:12,980 --> 00:06:13,439
What do you mean it doesn't count?

139
00:06:13,579 --> 00:06:14,160
One more.

140
00:06:14,839 --> 00:06:15,279
Fine.

141
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:16,680
Three.

142
00:06:17,339 --> 00:06:17,699
Two.

143
00:06:18,699 --> 00:06:19,040
One.

144
00:06:20,339 --> 00:06:21,060
Three again.

145
00:06:22,699 --> 00:06:23,959
