151
00:06:39,060 --> 00:06:39,620
So amazing!

152
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:45,319
Bite.

153
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,420
Look at the sky.

154
00:06:48,019 --> 00:06:49,639
It's blue.

155
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:50,939
See?

156
00:06:51,060 --> 00:06:52,639
And the trees all around,

157
00:06:52,639 --> 00:06:53,339
the grass,

158
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,819
they're all green.

159
00:06:57,860 --> 00:06:59,540
Mom, I'm heading to the river.

160
00:06:59,899 --> 00:07:00,699
Look.

161
00:07:01,199 --> 00:07:02,339
Over twenty years ago,

162
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,439
