169
00:07:22,779 --> 00:07:23,939
Don't cry, don't cry.

170
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:27,360
Little Tiger.

171
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,120
There, there.

172
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,939
Sucking your little hand, huh?

173
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:35,480
Baby.

174
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:38,560
Don't cry, don't cry.

175
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,740
