179
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,740
Come give me a hand.

180
00:07:51,759 --> 00:07:52,120
Okay.

181
00:07:53,019 --> 00:07:53,480
Grandma's here.

182
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:55,439
There you go.

183
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:00,300
Sweet little one.

184
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,540
Uncle Yang

185
00:08:25,939 --> 00:08:26,620
This one's more

186
00:08:44,700 --> 00:08:45,379
Wait, Uncle Yang, this...

187
00:08:45,620 --> 00:08:46,440
