197
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:33,980
Pack up

198
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:37,299
Sure, Uncle Yang

199
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:39,480
I'll take good care of Bite

200
00:10:03,779 --> 00:10:04,379
