205
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:12,759
How disgraceful!

206
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,320
You're not going.

207
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,700
Those two kids just started getting somewhere,

208
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,879
