209
00:10:18,019 --> 00:10:18,559
Put that back.

210
00:10:18,639 --> 00:10:19,139
You're not going.

211
00:10:19,519 --> 00:10:20,059
You really...

212
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:20,600
As long as I'm here,

213
00:10:20,779 --> 00:10:21,700
you're not stepping out that door today.

214
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:24,000
Fine, fine, fine.

215
00:10:24,059 --> 00:10:24,820
I'll bear it, I'll bear it, I'll bear it.

216
00:10:25,379 --> 00:10:26,580
For my granddaughter, I'll bear it.

217
00:10:26,740 --> 00:10:27,399
I'll bear it.

218
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:30,980
Aren't you just so noble.

219
00:10:40,580 --> 00:10:41,519
Xiaowei!

220
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:45,039
Xiaowei, be careful!

221
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:07,139
Xiaofang

222
00:11:07,679 --> 00:11:08,899
You just had a baby

223
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:10,139
Shouldn't you rest a bit more?

224
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:13,100
I've gotta earn money for formula

225
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:15,779
But isn't Xiaowei earning for you?

226
00:11:16,620 --> 00:11:17,860
Just the other day at the amusement park

227
00:11:17,940 --> 00:11:18,700
I saw him working there

228
00:11:21,539 --> 00:11:22,700
I don't rely on anyone to make money

229
00:11:22,759 --> 00:11:23,419
I rely on myself

230
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:25,600
I think Xiaowei's really turned out great

231
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:28,600
He's a completely different person now

232
00:11:28,919 --> 00:11:30,820
If my man could be like Xiaowei

233
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:31,879
and step up like that

234
00:11:32,539 --> 00:11:34,580
