235
00:11:34,980 --> 00:11:36,360
If Xiaowei's really changed for the better

236
00:11:36,620 --> 00:11:37,799
and you two already have history

237
00:11:37,820 --> 00:11:38,740
and know each other so well

238
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:39,820
maybe getting back with your old flame

239
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:40,820
would actually be pretty sweet

240
00:11:42,460 --> 00:11:43,139
Tell me

241
00:11:43,379 --> 00:11:45,299
