242
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:47,039
does he actually grow up?

243
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:48,019
and become more steady?

244
00:11:48,779 --> 00:11:50,240
Just look at my man

245
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,740
My son's three years old now

246
00:11:52,139 --> 00:11:53,980
He's never fed him once

247
00:11:53,980 --> 00:11:55,580
Never changed a diaper once

248
00:11:56,299 --> 00:11:57,759
So what's the point of having a man?

249
00:11:58,259 --> 00:12:00,059
Anyway, I've figured it out

250
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,419
When it comes to daily life

251
00:12:01,460 --> 00:12:03,039
finding a man who shares the load

252
00:12:03,299 --> 00:12:04,419
beats anything else

253
00:12:19,259 --> 00:12:20,759
What's this? Why are you acting mysterious?

254
00:12:20,759 --> 00:12:21,460
Get in there, hurry up!

255
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,399
Wait for me, wait for me!

256
00:12:22,399 --> 00:12:22,919
