257
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:24,340
Sky lanterns!

258
00:12:33,940 --> 00:12:34,720
Let me see, let me see!

259
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,120
A starry-sky ceiling!

260
00:12:42,899 --> 00:12:45,080
You did a pretty good job on this ceiling.

261
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:45,980
Who knew?

262
00:12:46,519 --> 00:12:48,460
You're quite the romantic, you rascal.

263
00:12:49,980 --> 00:12:51,960
Bite, look at the stars!

264
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,019
Isn't it pretty?

265
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,620
Not bad at all, Xiaowei.

266
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:28,960
So...

267
00:13:29,179 --> 00:13:30,960
Xiaofang just had her baby, you know

268
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,700
