276
00:13:49,820 --> 00:13:50,379
Second shelf

277
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:51,480
Anything else?

278
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:52,639
Nope

279
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:53,379
Okay

280
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:54,620
Well then...

281
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:56,600
I'll hang up now

282
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,360
