289
00:14:12,419 --> 00:14:13,279
and you just expect me to come back

290
00:14:13,299 --> 00:14:14,779
and serve you like a maid, huh?

291
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:16,980
Why on earth should I cook for you?

292
00:14:17,259 --> 00:14:18,980
Do I owe you something?

293
00:14:20,919 --> 00:14:21,639
What's gotten into you?

