00:27:01,519 --> 00:27:02,279
You voted for number seven?

584
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:03,119
Auntie.

585
00:27:03,500 --> 00:27:04,220
Who did you vote for?

586
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:05,140
I voted for number seven.

587
00:27:05,519 --> 00:27:06,779
Why'd you vote for her?

588
00:27:06,819 --> 00:27:07,759
Which number did you all vote for?

589
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:08,539
I voted for number five.

590
00:27:09,660 --> 00:27:10,339
Number seven.

591
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:10,839
Look, look!

592
00:27:10,880 --> 00:27:11,859
Number seven's pretty, right?

593
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:12,740
Nineteen.

594
00:27:12,980 --> 00:27:13,539
Number seven.

595
00:27:13,900 --> 00:27:14,359
Number seven.

596
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:15,119
Look at mine.

597
00:27:15,279 --> 00:27:15,960
I voted for Xiaofang.

598
00:27:16,339 --> 00:27:17,039
I knew it.

599
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:18,160
She definitely voted for Xiaofang.

600
00:27:18,339 --> 00:27:20,180
I think for a mom,

601
00:27:20,619 --> 00:27:22,079
whatever's best for the child,

602
00:27:22,079 --> 00:27:23,420
that's the right choice, obviously.

603
00:27:23,740 --> 00:27:24,380
Take me, for example.

604
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:25,519
Back when I had my little one,

605
00:27:25,839 --> 00:27:26,680
I had no milk.

606
00:27:26,960 --> 00:27:27,700
I forced myself

607
00:27:27,700 --> 00:27:28,440
to gain 20 jin,

608
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,559
just to get my milk to come in.

609
00:27:29,619 --> 00:27:30,759
Why'd you vote for her?

610
00:27:30,839 --> 00:27:31,920
I'm number six.

611
00:27:32,119 --> 00:27:32,880
Then I'll vote for number nine.

612
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:34,079
You didn't vote for your wife?

613
00:27:34,500 --> 00:27:35,259
I voted for Xiaofang.

614
00:27:35,299 --> 00:27:35,759
What about you?

615
00:27:36,119 --> 00:27:37,119
I'll just follow along, then.

616
00:27:37,279 --> 00:27:38,660
I don't really have an opinion anyway.

617
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:40,259
What's this?

618
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:43,599
The Most Beautiful Mom vote.

619
00:27:44,420 --> 00:27:45,319
I even voted for you.

620
00:27:45,319 --> 00:27:46,500
I'll file a complaint instead.

621
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:51,720
This photo of Xiaofang

622
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:52,799
is pretty nice, actually.

623
00:27:56,599 --> 00:27:57,140
Complaint.

624
00:27:58,319 --> 00:27:59,880
I know these days everyone says

625
00:28:00,140 --> 00:28:00,819
that a mom

626
00:28:00,819 --> 00:28:02,140
should be a bit kinder to herself.

627
00:28:02,519 --> 00:28:03,299
Take Xiaofang, for example.

628
00:28:03,619 --> 00:28:04,359
She just finished her confinement

629
00:28:04,359 --> 00:28:05,140
and already weaned the baby.

630
00:28:08,539 --> 00:28:09,119
Xiaofang.

631
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:10,819
Xiaochao says you've already weaned.

632
00:28:11,279 --> 00:28:12,759
Yeah, when it's time to wean, you wean.

633
00:28:13,420 --> 00:28:14,759
What were you thinking?

634
00:28:15,539 --> 00:28:17,200
If you have milk, you breastfeed.

635
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,920
If not, formula's just fine.

636
00:28:19,359 --> 00:28:20,579
I think a mom

637
00:28:20,579 --> 00:28:21,500
has to be comfortable herself.

638
00:28:21,500 --> 00:28:22,279
Once she's comfortable,

639
00:28:22,279 --> 00:28:23,000
she's in a good state.

640
00:28:23,099 --> 00:28:23,839
And once she's in a good state,

641
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:24,980
she can be a better mom.

642
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:47,799
You really weaned him?

643
00:28:48,700 --> 00:28:49,160
That's right.

644
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:51,059
Then what about all your soup?

645
00:28:51,619 --> 00:28:52,480
I gave it to Dandan to drink.

646
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,500
I added a little salt to it.

647
00:28:53,500 --> 00:28:54,359
He said it tasted pretty good.

648
00:28:54,819 --> 00:28:55,940
No wonder Dandan lately

649
00:28:55,940 --> 00:28:57,180
has put on a few pounds.

650
00:28:57,859 --> 00:28:58,539
If you've weaned him,

651
00:28:58,799 --> 00:28:59,640
what does Bite drink?

652
00:29:00,099 --> 00:29:00,799
Formula, of course.

653
00:29:01,019 --> 00:29:02,000
Where did you get formula?

654
00:29:05,559 --> 00:29:06,099
No need to say more.

655
00:29:07,279 --> 00:29:08,299
You're in cahoots, right?

656
00:29:08,980 --> 00:29:10,700
You've really gone too far.

657
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:11,619
That's a bit much, isn't it?

658
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:13,660
How can I count as an outsider?

659
00:29:13,960 --> 00:29:15,220
I'm the little grandpa now.

660
00:29:15,420 --> 00:29:16,920
You think I'd let Bite go hungry?

661
00:29:17,539 --> 00:29:18,539
And you, if you're weaning him,

662
00:29:18,539 --> 00:29:19,980
why didn't you tell everyone?

663
00:29:22,759 --> 00:29:24,359
I told you all long ago.

664
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:25,259
But you two aunts,

665
00:29:25,259 --> 00:29:26,819
neither of you took it seriously.

666
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:29,940
Look,

667
00:29:30,720 --> 00:29:32,099
you can control me for a while,

668
00:29:32,099 --> 00:29:33,259
but not for my whole life.

669
00:29:33,299 --> 00:29:34,279
So don't bother worrying.

670
00:29:34,319 --> 00:29:35,200
I've got my own mind.

671
00:29:35,480 --> 00:29:36,079
Someone like you,

672
00:29:36,119 --> 00:29:37,200
entering Most Beautiful Mom?

673
00:29:37,619 --> 00:29:38,279
If it were me,

674
00:29:38,660 --> 00:29:39,779
I'd disqualify you.

675
00:29:40,359 --> 00:29:41,380
Too bad you're not qualified to.

676
00:29:42,319 --> 00:29:43,759
Aren't the results out at ten?

677
00:29:44,180 --> 00:29:44,920
Yeah, that's right.

678
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:54,119
Here it comes, here it comes!

679
00:29:58,380 --> 00:29:58,759
Look.

680
00:30:03,619 --> 00:30:05,279
Moms don't need beauty contests,

681
00:30:06,180 --> 00:30:07,160
and certainly no "most."

682
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,180
Everyone has only one mom.

683
00:30:09,279 --> 00:30:09,960
How can you compare?

684
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:11,920
I don't get what this event

685
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:12,920
is even about.

686
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:13,859
Look how gorgeous Ma is!

687
00:30:16,859 --> 00:30:17,400
You lot,

688
00:30:18,200 --> 00:30:19,799
you all voted for me, right?

689
00:30:20,079 --> 00:30:21,420
Voted, definitely voted.

690
00:30:22,539 --> 00:30:24,259
You three didn't vote for yourselves, did you?

691
00:30:31,980 --> 00:30:32,700
Where's Dandan?

692
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:34,380
Where did Dandan go?

693
00:30:34,660 --> 00:30:35,579
Dandan!

694
00:30:37,299 --> 00:30:38,099
Bite's crying.

695
00:30:41,099 --> 00:30:42,599
I'll go call Old Miao back.

696
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:01,339
See, I keep my word, don't I?

697
00:31:01,839 --> 00:31:03,539
The Most Beautiful Mom won prize money.

698
00:31:03,779 --> 00:31:05,420
Half went to my granddaughter.

699
00:31:05,759 --> 00:31:06,339
And the other half,

700
00:31:06,619 --> 00:31:08,660
treats you old gals to a meal.

701
00:31:09,259 --> 00:31:11,339
Thank you, thank you, thank you!

702
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:13,279
We've still got real pull, huh!

703
00:31:13,980 --> 00:31:14,400
Let's drink to that!

704
00:31:14,519 --> 00:31:15,460
The moment I saw you were in it,

705
00:31:15,559 --> 00:31:16,859
of course I had to support it!

706
00:31:17,059 --> 00:31:18,440
The dance group, the grocery group,

707
00:31:18,579 --> 00:31:19,559
the choir group,

708
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:21,059
I posted it in every single one.

709
00:31:21,279 --> 00:31:22,279
Thank you!

710
00:31:22,559 --> 00:31:24,180
Their one or two years on the job,

711
00:31:24,359 --> 00:31:26,140
against our fifty or sixty years,

712
00:31:26,279 --> 00:31:27,279
how can they even compare?

713
00:31:27,339 --> 00:31:27,880
Exactly!

714
00:31:28,819 --> 00:31:29,940
When we were already mothers,

715
00:31:30,079 --> 00:31:31,500
they were still nursing.

716
00:31:31,579 --> 00:31:33,359
And they nursed on our milk, too!

717
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:35,559
Today,

718
00:31:35,720 --> 00:31:37,240
I got some fancy foreign stuff.

719
00:31:37,460 --> 00:31:38,700
Everyone dig in!

720
00:31:38,839 --> 00:31:39,119
Great!

721
00:31:39,119 --> 00:31:39,839
See if it suits your taste.

722
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:40,359
Sure!

723
00:31:40,779 --> 00:31:41,059
Good!

724
00:31:41,059 --> 00:31:41,519
Delicious!

725
00:31:41,619 --> 00:31:42,200
So good, so good!

726
00:31:42,359 --> 00:31:43,640
All right, come on, cheers, cheers!

727
00:31:43,759 --> 00:31:45,059
Come on, cheers!

728
00:31:45,759 --> 00:31:47,299
Cheers, cheers!

729
00:31:47,380 --> 00:31:48,500
Using foreign words now, are we!

730
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:49,660
Come on, come on!

731
00:31:50,480 --> 00:31:51,119
With these two hands of mine,

732
00:31:51,119 --> 00:31:52,099
I don't even know which one to use!

733
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:54,240
Yan'er, in my heart,

734
00:31:54,619 --> 00:31:56,160
you're the real Most Beautiful Mom.

735
00:31:57,900 --> 00:31:59,220
Being beautiful in your heart,

736
00:31:59,259 --> 00:32:00,200
what good does that do me?

737
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:12,720
Hey

738
00:32:13,559 --> 00:32:14,380
How am I beautiful?

739
00:32:15,319 --> 00:32:16,720
How can you even ask that?

740
00:32:18,559 --> 00:32:19,980
Xiaofang told me

741
00:32:20,940 --> 00:32:22,319
that you paid off my debt for me

742
00:32:25,460 --> 00:32:26,259
That's beautiful

743
00:32:28,559 --> 00:32:29,420
Well-deserved

744
00:32:31,359 --> 00:32:32,079
That was...

745
00:32:32,500 --> 00:32:34,039
cold hard cash I poured into it

746
00:32:34,859 --> 00:32:35,900
Didn't you say it yourself?

747
00:32:36,500 --> 00:32:38,339
Money should be spent where it counts

748
00:32:38,859 --> 00:32:40,220
Well, this time it counted, didn't it?

749
00:32:42,839 --> 00:32:44,220
They say mother and daughter are of one heart

750
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,099
I only spend my money

751
00:32:46,839 --> 00:32:48,160
where it counts for you

752
00:32:49,359 --> 00:32:50,440
Come home for dinner tonight

753
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:51,960
I'll make you something good

754
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:52,779
Okay

755
00:32:57,299 --> 00:32:58,559
Making something good, huh?

756
00:33:00,259 --> 00:33:01,039
What's going on over here?

757
00:33:02,079 --> 00:33:02,900
Who cares about all that

758
00:33:09,720 --> 00:33:10,519
This old Qu lady

759
00:33:10,539 --> 00:33:11,720
actually got first place

760
00:33:12,019 --> 00:33:13,480
Someone must have canvassed votes for her

761
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:16,400
No, that's well-deserved

762
00:33:16,660 --> 00:33:18,000
You think everyone's like you?

763
00:33:19,579 --> 00:33:21,279
Xiaofang really did wean the baby

764
00:33:25,380 --> 00:33:25,700
Ma

765
00:33:26,500 --> 00:33:27,079
Xiaowei

766
00:33:27,680 --> 00:33:28,980
So, Xiaofang,

767
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:31,019
why did you stop breastfeeding Bite?

768
00:33:31,579 --> 00:33:33,059
Is he getting enough nutrition?

769
00:33:34,220 --> 00:33:35,079
If it's not enough,

770
00:33:35,259 --> 00:33:36,480
bring Bite over to our place

771
00:33:37,119 --> 00:33:38,440
We'll hire a lactation consultant or something

772
00:33:39,579 --> 00:33:40,140
Don't worry

773
00:33:41,019 --> 00:33:41,940
Formula is perfectly fine

774
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:43,079
I support Xiaofang

775
00:34:09,019 --> 00:34:09,320
Ma

776
00:34:10,119 --> 00:34:10,579
Hold on a sec

777
00:34:12,039 --> 00:34:12,420
What is it?

778
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:13,519
Come... come here

779
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:18,340
What for?

780
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:22,639
This...

781
00:34:24,780 --> 00:34:25,340
This is...

782
00:34:26,800 --> 00:34:27,519
For me?

783
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:30,280
You didn't enter the Most Beautiful Mom contest

784
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:31,079
but my one vote

785
00:34:31,099 --> 00:34:32,179
would definitely go to you

786
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,559
Most Beautiful Mom

787
00:35:30,699 --> 00:35:31,340
What are you crying for?

788
00:35:33,860 --> 00:35:34,940
Thank you, son.

789
00:35:45,320 --> 00:35:46,639
Mom loves these flowers

790
00:35:58,639 --> 00:35:59,619
Mom likes them

791
00:36:01,619 --> 00:36:03,980
What sorry-looking flowers, so embarrassing

792
00:36:05,480 --> 00:36:07,059
Doesn't even think to get me a bouquet.

793
00:36:09,340 --> 00:36:11,440
The sun smiles at me

794
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:13,719
The flowers are all in bloom

795
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:16,519
The little birds sing tra-la-la

796
00:36:16,820 --> 00:36:19,659
I'll put on my little backpack

797
00:36:20,219 --> 00:36:21,739
Old Qi, come take a look

798
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:22,539
Nice, nice

799
00:36:22,539 --> 00:36:23,380
Does it look good or not?

800
00:36:25,699 --> 00:36:26,320
Xiaofang

801
00:36:26,820 --> 00:36:28,820
I was so nervous during that interview

802
00:36:29,119 --> 00:36:29,780
I didn't mean to

803
00:36:29,780 --> 00:36:31,219
blurt out that you'd weaned the baby

804
00:36:31,219 --> 00:36:32,420
in front of the whole village

805
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,460
I'm sorry

806
00:36:34,239 --> 00:36:35,079
It's okay

807
00:36:37,260 --> 00:36:38,539
Xiaofang, you have no idea

808
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:39,659
I felt so awkward about it

809
00:36:39,699 --> 00:36:40,719
I've been too embarrassed to come by

810
00:36:41,019 --> 00:36:41,739
It's no big deal

811
00:36:42,340 --> 00:36:43,800
As punishment, you have to buy me

812
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:45,480
this many watermelons

813
00:36:46,840 --> 00:36:48,480
You trying to bankrupt me?

814
00:36:51,500 --> 00:36:52,440
Sure, sure, sure

815
00:36:53,460 --> 00:36:54,619
Just imagine that sauce

816
00:36:54,679 --> 00:36:55,840
once it's cooked all soft and tender

817
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:57,960
then coating those spicy ribs

818
00:36:58,280 --> 00:36:59,280
I'm getting hungry already

819
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:00,179
Me too

820
00:37:00,179 --> 00:37:01,260
Bite's mom, Doudou's mom

821
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:02,159
Zhang Quan's wife

822
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:04,119
You went up the mountain digging herbs?

823
00:37:05,400 --> 00:37:06,280
We're planning tomorrow too

824
00:37:06,320 --> 00:37:07,340
to go up and dig some

825
00:37:07,500 --> 00:37:09,159
Were you on the east side or the west?

826
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:10,380
So we can avoid your spot

827
00:37:10,420 --> 00:37:11,440
and not come back empty-handed

828
00:37:12,199 --> 00:37:13,139
We were over on the east side

829
00:37:13,139 --> 00:37:14,519
Just head west and you'll be fine

830
00:37:14,679 --> 00:37:15,860
Okay, thanks

831
00:37:15,940 --> 00:37:16,539
No problem

832
00:37:17,579 --> 00:37:18,019
See you

833
00:37:19,079 --> 00:37:19,519
Xiaofang

834
00:37:19,559 --> 00:37:20,900
Where was that restaurant you mentioned?

835
00:37:23,179 --> 00:37:24,139
What's wrong, Xiaofang?

836
00:37:24,639 --> 00:37:26,179
It's just nicer to be called Xiaofang

837
00:37:26,739 --> 00:37:28,239
Isn't that what they call you once you have kids?

838
00:37:28,460 --> 00:37:29,760
You'll get used to it after a while

839
00:37:30,079 --> 00:37:31,659
That's just how everyone in our village does it

840
00:37:31,659 --> 00:37:32,519
One listen and you know

841
00:37:32,519 --> 00:37:33,320
whose wife you are

842
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,280
whose kid's mom you are

843
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:35,480
Even though right now I'm

844
00:37:35,519 --> 00:37:36,199
Bite's mom

845
00:37:36,199 --> 00:37:37,199
I'm still Yang Xiaofang too

846
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:38,119
Just like these herbs

847
00:37:38,119 --> 00:37:39,219
they each have their own name

848
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:41,280
Astragalus, Scutellaria root, Cassia seed

849
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:41,880
Gastrodia elata

850
00:37:42,079 --> 00:37:43,019
What you're saying

851
00:37:43,019 --> 00:37:44,619
I never thought about it before

852
00:37:44,860 --> 00:37:45,480
Think about it

853
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:46,079
My mom

854
00:37:46,260 --> 00:37:46,980
My grandma

855
00:37:47,139 --> 00:37:48,179
they all get called that way

856
00:37:49,739 --> 00:37:51,199
From now on, anyone dares call me Zhang Quan's wife

857
00:37:51,199 --> 00:37:51,860
I'll get mad at them

858
00:37:54,519 --> 00:37:55,079
Wang Lezhu

859
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:56,480
They're calling you

860
00:37:57,300 --> 00:37:58,340
Wang Lezhu

861
00:37:59,139 --> 00:37:59,519
Here

862
00:38:00,420 --> 00:38:01,079
Li Jingchao

863
00:38:01,300 --> 00:38:01,619
Here

864
00:38:02,139 --> 00:38:03,300
Yang Xiaofang

865
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:04,260
Here

866
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:53,079
Nice weather today, Xiaofang.

867
00:38:56,159 --> 00:38:56,820
Auntie.

868
00:38:58,300 --> 00:38:58,920
Come on up.

869
00:39:00,460 --> 00:39:00,800
No, thanks.

870
00:39:00,820 --> 00:39:02,260
I left the stove on at home.

871
00:39:02,260 --> 00:39:03,440
It's fine, come on up.

872
00:39:08,480 --> 00:39:09,440
I'm not bothering you, am I?

873
00:39:11,739 --> 00:39:12,659
The baby just woke up.

874
00:39:15,159 --> 00:39:15,920
Sweetie.

875
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:18,900
Sweetie.

876
00:39:20,760 --> 00:39:21,599
Look at these tiny hands.

877
00:39:23,539 --> 00:39:24,320
She smells so sweet.

878
00:39:27,820 --> 00:39:29,219
Auntie, here, hold her.

879
00:39:30,320 --> 00:39:30,659
Me?

880
00:39:35,420 --> 00:39:35,780
Here.

881
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:43,239
Who's holding you, sweetie?

882
00:39:43,519 --> 00:39:44,699
Look at those baby eyes.

883
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:51,500
Sweetie.

884
00:39:53,480 --> 00:39:53,880
There, there.

885
00:39:55,159 --> 00:39:56,500
Still a bit shy, huh?

886
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:03,699
Who's holding you, sweetie?

887
00:40:05,159 --> 00:40:07,739
The sun smiles at me.

888
00:40:08,679 --> 00:40:11,139
What a beautiful baby.

889
00:40:11,760 --> 00:40:14,139
Bite carries her little backpack.

890
00:40:17,300 --> 00:40:19,739
Off to school.

891
00:40:22,480 --> 00:40:23,320
Sweetie.

892
00:40:26,139 --> 00:40:26,840
Sweetie.

893
00:40:27,679 --> 00:40:28,219
Look.

894
00:40:28,860 --> 00:40:30,380
Whose house is that over there?

895
00:40:37,619 --> 00:40:38,199
Auntie.

896
00:40:38,860 --> 00:40:40,199
Bite is your granddaughter too.

897
00:40:40,579 --> 00:40:41,820
Whenever you miss Bite,

898
00:40:41,880 --> 00:40:42,920
just come over and see her.

899
00:40:50,179 --> 00:40:51,139
Thank you, Xiaofang.

900
00:40:55,099 --> 00:40:56,300
Look how chubby this baby is.

901
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:01,539
And those big eyes.

902
00:41:01,880 --> 00:41:02,719
She looks just like you.

903
00:41:04,699 --> 00:41:05,340
Come, come.

904
00:41:05,940 --> 00:41:07,079
Better let Mommy hold her.

905
00:41:25,380 --> 00:41:26,000
Where'd you run off to?

906
00:41:28,460 --> 00:41:29,360
Didn't you see it all?

907
00:41:29,739 --> 00:41:30,280
Traitor.

908
00:41:34,099 --> 00:41:36,139
I brought you back some spoils.

909
00:41:37,539 --> 00:41:37,920
Look.

910
00:41:39,199 --> 00:41:39,800
Look, look, look.

911
00:41:40,260 --> 00:41:41,380
Isn't she just so chubby?

912
00:41:42,480 --> 00:41:43,099
Those little feet.

913
00:41:46,320 --> 00:41:47,400
Isn't this granddaughter adorable?

914
00:41:47,579 --> 00:41:48,619
Yes, yes.

915
00:41:50,059 --> 00:41:50,440
Adorable.

916
00:41:51,860 --> 00:41:53,480
You should go hold her sometime too.

917
00:41:55,539 --> 00:41:56,340
I couldn't care less.

918
00:41:57,360 --> 00:41:58,219
I've got a grandson.

919
00:42:04,119 --> 00:42:05,539
Look at Grandpa's little ambition.

920
00:42:30,400 --> 00:42:31,980
I think this little Bite here...

921
00:42:32,519 --> 00:42:33,719
really looks like our Xiaowei.

922
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:35,039
And a little like me too.

923
00:42:36,019 --> 00:42:36,539
Like you?

924
00:42:36,639 --> 00:42:37,519
Have you even looked at her?

925
00:42:37,900 --> 00:42:38,300
No, no.

926
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:39,619
Look at her eyes, they're just like mine.

927
00:42:39,679 --> 00:42:40,840
Not like certain people's beady little eyes.

928
00:42:41,960 --> 00:42:42,940
You must be tired from holding her.

929
00:42:44,000 --> 00:42:44,579
Take a little break.

930
00:42:44,599 --> 00:42:45,320
Let me hold her for you.

931
00:42:46,659 --> 00:42:47,699
Can you even manage her?

932
00:42:47,739 --> 00:42:48,880
Give her here, of course I can.

933
00:42:48,940 --> 00:42:49,800
All right, hand her over then.

934
00:42:50,519 --> 00:42:51,400
Did you wash your hands?

935
00:42:52,320 --> 00:42:53,219
I'll go wash them right now.

936
00:43:23,440 --> 00:43:24,420
Your uncle's found you

937
00:43:24,420 --> 00:43:25,139
a whole new opportunity

938
00:43:25,139 --> 00:43:26,420
You might get rich

939
00:43:26,639 --> 00:43:27,960
I'm really optimistic

940
00:43:27,960 --> 00:43:29,400
about these herbal packs of yours

941
00:43:29,679 --> 00:43:30,880
But it feels like the production capacity

942
00:43:30,880 --> 00:43:31,679
is a bit lacking

943
00:43:32,039 --> 00:43:33,139
So I'm hoping the two of us

944
00:43:33,400 --> 00:43:34,320
can form a powerful alliance

945
00:43:34,320 --> 00:43:34,900
Forget it

946
00:43:36,300 --> 00:43:37,099
Do you think

947
00:43:37,219 --> 00:43:38,960
Xiaofang and Xiaowei still have a chance?

948
00:43:39,079 --> 00:43:40,380
I actually kind of like Xiaowei

949
00:43:40,460 --> 00:43:41,679
What's the point of him liking her?

950
00:43:41,840 --> 00:43:42,539
What matters is

951
00:43:42,639 --> 00:43:44,159
Xiaofang has to like him

952
00:43:44,300 --> 00:43:46,639
Just worry about your own business

953
00:43:46,860 --> 00:43:47,840
Get a divorce if you want to

954
00:43:48,039 --> 00:43:49,679
Your own happiness is what matters most

955
00:43:50,400 --> 00:43:51,300
Marry me

956
00:43:52,099 --> 00:43:52,699
Oh my god
